transcript.text: Hello today we will learn about new feature Product Image Gallery Enhanced in version 7.3.
In the previous version we introduced a feature where when a customer selects a specific additional options attribute, the product image bound with the option was displayed.
In this release we added one more option through which you can bind the product images with the additional options instead of the attributes.
Through this you can showcase all the attributes of an additional option in a single image to your customers.
You can configure different images for each additional option.
When you click on gallery settings it will give a pop up to select option wise.
Now see for example if we upload image for additional option corners which shows rounded and squared corners.
Now when we check on the front end side if we select options corners the gallery image changes automatically.
Please note this additional option wise gallery image feature will work only with drop down type of attributes.
Thanks for your time to watching this video.
